{"type":"message","id":"f1ec2db8","parentId":"ead5e002","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:08:21.187Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_jzl90tmdbe8yshuod6y4p860","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260329.json."}],"details":{"diff":"  1 {\n  2   \"task\": \"openclaw_daily_news\",\n  3   \"created_at\": \"2026-03-29 08:00:01\",\n- 4   \"status\": \"pending\",\n+ 4   \"status\": \"completed\",\n  5   \"instructions\": \"搜索 OpenClaw 相关最新资讯，整理并生成一篇精美的微信公众号文章。\",\n  6   \"steps\": [\n  7     \"使用 web_search 搜索 'OpenClaw' 最新资讯（近7天内）\",\n  8     \"筛选2-3条最有价值的新闻/动态\",\n    ...","firstChangedLine":4},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774742901185}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2f51781","parentId":"f1ec2db8","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:08:48.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 📰 OpenClaw 每日资讯已生成\n\n已完成今日（2026-03-29）OpenClaw 资讯推送任务：\n\n- 📄 文章已保存至：`/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_20260329.md`\n- ✅ 任务状态已更新为 `completed`\n\n## 内容摘要\n\n本期内容整理了 **2026.3.13** 版本的主要更新：\n\n- 📱 移动端体验优化，Android 和 iOS 引导流程改进\n- 🌐 浏览器自动化增强，支持 Chrome DevTools MCP 附加模式\n- 🐳 Docker 时区配置支持\n- 📊 仪表盘性能优化，避免 UI 冻结\n- 🔒 多项安全修复，包括设备配对和执行审批加固\n- 感谢社区 20+ 贡献者的参与\n\n可以直接拿去发公众号啦！✌️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":23906,"output":222,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24128,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774742901188}}
